HEADWORD: Blancard
<hw>Blan"card</hw> <pr>(bl⟦acr⟧⟦nsm⟧"k⟦etil⟧rd)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[F., fr. <ets>blanc</ets> white.]</ety> <def>A kind of linen cloth
